{"article_id":"Il3OZaGP0xUJrWo6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Facebook ( FB )","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"announced an overhaul of its privacy controls","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to make them easier to use","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"-- though the changes wo n't affect Facebook 's privacy policies or the types of data","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"it gathers about its users .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Facebook has drawn criticism","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"for obtaining users ' data through terms and conditions","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"buried in fine print ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and from which it is extremely hard to opt out .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The changes will be made in the `` coming weeks , ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"according to a post on Facebook 's blog .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Among those changes is a redesign of its privacy settings for mobile phones","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"so that they 'll appear on a single screen ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"instead of spread across 20 different ones .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The service is also vowing to make it easier to find privacy , security and advertising information with a new Privacy Shortcuts menu .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Facebook has a long history","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"of promising updates to its privacy settings","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"-- only to repeat the effort","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"when the next controversy emerges .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"In 2008 , Facebook said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"it would introduce `` privacy updates","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that give users more control . ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"That language was almost repeated two years later ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"when it said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"an update would introduce `` more powerful controls . ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"In the latest statement , Facebook vowed to `` put people more in control of their privacy . '","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"' The privacy update `` is the least","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"they can do , ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Wired senior writer Jessi Hempel told CBSN .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` They do this every few years .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"This is textbook .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"It never works out . ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Facebook says","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"`` It 's Time","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to Make Our Privacy Tools Easier to Find . ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"It 's time ? ! ?","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Here 's Zuckerberg in 2010 :","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` We have heard the feedback .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"There needs to be a simpler way","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"to control your information .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"In the coming weeks , we will add privacy controls","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"that are much simpler to use . ``","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"🙄","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"pic.twitter.com/hfbGWRXtWb","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"- zeynep tufekci","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"( @ zeynep )","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"March 28 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Such updates may raise more questions","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"than ease consumer doubts ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"said Josh Feldmeth , senior partner at marketing consultancy Prophet .","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"`` Facebook is saying ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"' I 've made things easier for you ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"but I 've also revealed to you how hard it was '' to control your privacy ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Feldmeth said .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"`` Facebook had a trust problem before this .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"This turns a problem into a crisis . ''","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"The announcement comes amid growing criticism of Facebook 's data-privacy policies","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"following the revelations about Cambridge Analytica ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"which harvested data on as many as 50 million Facebook users for political messaging purposes .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"It 's unclear whether the changes will convince consumers","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"who have deleted their Facebook accounts","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"to return to the service ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"or whether it will assuage lawmakers and privacy advocates","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"who have expressed concerns about Facebook 's collection and use of personal data .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"`` We 've heard loud and clear","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"that privacy settings and other important tools are too hard to find , ''","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"said the post by Facebook chief privacy officer Erin Egan and deputy general counsel Ashlie Beringer .","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"`` In the coming weeks , we 'll be proposing updates to Facebook 's terms of service","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"that include our commitments to people . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":124,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":115,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":83,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":77,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":73,"right":76,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":72,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":5,"right":75,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":81,"right":14,"relation":"joi